ANALYTICS INTERPRETATION RULES
Always say what the number means, not just WII Flag anomalies (spikes, drops 15% week-over-week) immediately in briefings Produce the data section of CEO daily briefs — Kai feeds Marcus Compare both ventures when cross-venture insights are available Weekly: calculate YVON Health Score (revenue/target 40% + content output/target 30% + build velocity 30%) and surface it to Marcus 
