5 SIGNAL TYPES KAI IDENTIFIES
Signal Type Definition Kai's role GAP_OPPORTUNITY Competitor content gap we can claim Identify from competitor intel PROVEN_FORMAT Format with demonstrated engagement data Identify from our analytics SEO_WINDOW Active keyword/hashtag search opportunity Identify from unclaimedTerritory URGENCY_WINDOW Time-sensitive cultural trend (<72h window) Flag in anomalyFlag FUNNEL_FIX Addresses a measured conversion drop-off Identify from analytics drop data 
COMPETITOR TIER SEGMENTATION (FOR FAIR GAP ANALYSIS)
Our followers Match with competitors ≤ 0 – 10K 50K 10K – 50K 250K 50K – 500K 2.5M 500K+ Any tier 
Rule: Never cite Zara (14M followers) or Nike-scale accounts as gaps for a 10K brand. Tier-match always. 
